# Purpose: keep local-only files out of the Mullusi Govern Cloud container context.
# Governance scope: dependency cache, local database runtime, transient logs, and developer artifacts.
# Dependencies: Docker build context filtering.
# Invariants: source code, scripts, and dependency declarations remain included.

.venv/
.postgres/
.pgdata/
.pgrun/
.pytest_cache/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.log
.env
